description: Sunlight reflects off a recently cleaned section of the keep wall, further illuminating the already bright corner area of the outer wall.  A few wooden stands and merchant tents have been set up here, taking advantage of the extra light to show off their goods.

Moonlight reflects off a recently cleaned section of the keep wall, further illuminating the torch lit corner area of the outer wall.  A few wooden stands and merchant tents have been set up here, taking advantage of the extra light to show off their goods.
title: [Guardian Keep, Outer Wall]
